{"tid":2119963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民不滿新「戴罩令」　稱生死有命","createTime":"2020-07-22T11:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:39:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0d1dbda4a3fded2aa5c8683bba944d1de0e718","tid":2119963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539288-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539288-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=d6f61e48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539288-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7c32afd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539288-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n明日起，市民必須在室內公眾地方戴口罩，包括商場、巴士總站及公共交通交匯處等，暫時為期兩周。<br />\n<br />\n在樂富的有蓋巴士總站，有乘客歡迎規定，她說街上仍有人拉低口罩或露出鼻，認為人人戴口罩屬基本責任，不應有法例規管才做。<br />\n<br />\n亦有市民在巴士站拉低口罩，他批評政府無理，他說經歷03年沙士也安然無恙，相信生死有命，現時上車才戴口罩，決定明天實施規例後再打算。<br />\n<br />\n在深水埗北河街街市，部分菜販拉低口罩叫賣，亦有排檔檔主無戴口罩。有戴上口罩的玉器檔主說，天氣熱需時適應，又建議政府擴大規管範圍時多作勸喻及體諒不同情況。"},{"pid":"1dfd66682df2ab25a1c75d3a499f70ff03eb1e17","tid":2119963,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:30:12.000Z","msg":"你生死有命係你既事<br />\n<br />\n我唔想比你累死"},{"pid":"9b9574748a19a4f9c62d0ff6b103ab771db8718b","tid":2119963,"uid":59818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuGYLEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuGYLEM.jpg&h=9e2b8416&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64d0b2e294005e452c00e7b64ea45a7fc376072c","tid":2119963,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔最愛戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}